Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.25,0:00:30.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}愛が愛を「重過ぎる」って理解を拒み
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.08,0:00:34.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}憎しみに　変わっていく前に…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.56,0:00:36.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}何もかもそうだろ?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.66,0:00:41.71,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}バツの悪い事情にはいつも蓋して
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.75,0:00:44.53,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}食わせ物のリアル
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.54,0:00:46.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}歪んだジレンマ時代で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.88,0:00:50.80,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}約束したはずの二人さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.81,0:00:55.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}気付かず通り過ぎて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.82,0:01:02.58,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}壊しあって　解り合ってたことも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.65,0:01:04.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}置き去りにした
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.49,0:01:07.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}これが成れの果てなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.98,0:01:12.35,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}認めないで　立ち向かったときも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.11,0:01:18.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}落ちて行く時のイメージから逃げ出せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.78,0:01:23.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}Ah　何度でも探し出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.46,0:01:30.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}君の目　その手の温もりを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.22,0:01:33.61,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}愛はいつも私を傷つけるだけ…って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.63,0:01:37.28,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}君はつぶやいて　信じる事が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.30,0:01:40.28,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}怖くて泣いたんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.29,0:01:42.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}弱さを知って強くなれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.67,0:01:46.24,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}恐れず信じることで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:51.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}本当の愛を知るのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.25,0:00:30.08,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}爱因爱而愈加沉重 却拒绝理解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.08,0:00:34.56,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}在爱变为恨之前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.56,0:00:36.66,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}所有一切皆是如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.66,0:00:41.71,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}窘迫的永远是这眼前的迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.72,0:00:44.53,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}仿佛被吞噬之物的写实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.54,0:00:46.84,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}在这被扭曲的进退两难之时代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.88,0:00:50.80,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}即使海誓山盟的两人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.81,0:00:55.15,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}也渐行着冷漠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.82,0:01:02.58,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}毁灭与理解之物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.65,0:01:04.43,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}早已被遗弃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.49,0:01:07.96,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}这难道是灭亡之尽头？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.98,0:01:12.35,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}否认这一切 挺身面对之时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.11,0:01:18.75,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}即将殒落之时 都不会逃离眼前的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.78,0:01:23.42,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}啊，无论如何也要找寻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.46,0:01:30.10,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}你的双眸 双手的温存
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.22,0:01:33.61,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}说什么「爱总是只给我带来伤害」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.63,0:01:37.28,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}君之低声细语 深信之言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.30,0:01:40.28,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}是在恐惧中哭泣么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.29,0:01:42.43,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}认识着软弱 渴望着坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.67,0:01:46.24,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}当不再恐惧而满怀信仰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:51.04,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}那将是真实的爱
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----ED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:24.10,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}純真さが シンプルな力に 変わる 世界に影をつくりだす
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.75,0:21:38.64,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}ガラスケ一スに横たわる 光の存在に触れたくても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.72,0:21:45.74,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}振り上げた手 降ろせなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:21:54.41,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}落ちるようにしゃがみこんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.54,0:22:02.73,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}Prototype boy 明日の理想だけで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.97,0:22:10.22,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}語り継ぐような 美談にもならないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.43,0:22:17.55,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}この体を失いそうな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.75,0:22:26.72,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}ギリギリの場所が 哀しいくらい似合ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:24.10,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}当纯真变为单纯的力量 世界由此诞生了影子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.75,0:21:38.64,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}穿透过玻璃橱 感触着这光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.72,0:21:45.74,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}举起的手无法放下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:21:54.41,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}却如同坠落般跌下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.54,0:22:02.73,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}Prototype boy 抛开明天的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.97,0:22:10.22,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}即便无法成为传承的美谈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.43,0:22:17.55,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}如同就要失去这副身躯一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.75,0:22:26.72,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}在极限的边缘 跌入悲伤的深渊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在4年前发生的阿扎帝斯坦的内乱中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.56,0:00:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同天行者组织的成员有过接触吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.03,0:00:07.21,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球联邦军 反政府势力监禁设施
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.56,0:00:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.73,0:00:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4年前也应该已经说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.95,0:00:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时和现在的情况不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.94,0:00:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的Gundam出现的现如今
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.34,0:00:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再一次 成为了最重要的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿扎帝斯坦王国 第一皇女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.09,0:00:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽娜·伊斯玛依露
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.62,0:02:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将联邦保安局
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.19,0:02:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,划归为独立治安维持部队的直辖组织
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.74,0:02:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经在议会上决定下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4000万人规模的军队…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.58,0:02:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其创设成为可能 完全是依靠维塔的情报统制
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能略尽微薄之力是我的光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.67,0:02:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦政府不能屈于一丝一毫的抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.39,0:02:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是为了即将到来的对话…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.71,0:02:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期待着诸位的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.85,0:02:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是此意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正是为此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.39,0:02:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才降生于这里的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忠实地执行着伊奥利亚·肖汉博格的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.33,0:02:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是别人都做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.75,0:02:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到的只有我们 变革者而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.75,0:02:46.28,Second,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1150,1008)}Innovator
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.80,0:02:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿扎帝斯坦的公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.12,0:02:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前明明一直丢在那里不管
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.01,0:02:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是又怎么心血来潮了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又不是不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.44,0:03:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在那里也有Gundam机师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起来 测试体E-57
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.18,0:03:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个男的么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.48,0:03:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这4年间都被拘押在这个监禁所里的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.21,0:03:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个Gundam的驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.41,0:03:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有受到我的脑量子波的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.04,0:03:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告里说原因是头部受的伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.64,0:03:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于 见到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.69,0:03:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然 还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.79,0:03:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.19,0:03:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.43,0:03:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在「全球」一直和你说话的阿雷鲁亚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.55,0:03:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字才不是什么玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.43,0:04:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你就是玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:02.20,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉格朗日L1点 资源卫星群
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS的战斗经验呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.61,0:04:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充其量乘过作业用的Walk Loader而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.33,0:04:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把一个彻底的外行带回来了么… 刹那这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做的事情还有一堆的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.54,0:04:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.81,0:04:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱的教官老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.37,0:04:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别拿我开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.84,0:04:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔·狄兰迪…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arios和Cherudim的收容怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.55,0:04:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是躲在房间里不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「并不是要回到天行者来」 一直这么嚷着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.65,0:04:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确如记录里所说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throne和我们 是在不同的立场上进行武力介入的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说不是一伙的?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:04:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也同样用Gundam杀过人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也让很多人遭遇了像我这样的境地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎恨你们是理所当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.14,0:05:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.07,0:05:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界原本明明是和平的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.82,0:05:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平的日子本应理所当然地继续下去的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.03,0:05:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的那份和平毁掉的就是你们!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.87,0:05:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要自己在和平之中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样就好了么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.82,0:05:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.59,0:05:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也不想遭遇不幸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转属A-LAWS之后 有什么不寻常的事情么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.43,0:05:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起平常也就是训练的量多一些而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.89,0:05:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.42,0:05:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.52,0:05:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超人机关的相关资料里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:05:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么人的名字叫玛丽的么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.42,0:05:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:05:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没收的所有资料我应该都过目了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 有任务了 我先挂断了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.99,0:06:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.38,0:06:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.32,0:06:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉 主力部队到达了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 联络过来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让全员各自就位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据任务计划进入警备状态
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.66,0:06:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联络先遣队的皮瑞斯中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长翅膀那架的驾驶员…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是被监禁在那个地方的么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转交给上层部之后 再也没有下来任何情报了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS知道这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.07,0:06:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如Level 2的情报所述
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认机师的生存
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.77,0:06:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS也在集结起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您意下如何? 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.30,0:06:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对策这边会开始进行 你回来就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.94,0:06:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽 为什么改了名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那样的言行…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 是把另一个人格…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从王留美来的加密通信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.86,0:07:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「在人革领地 反政府势力监禁设施…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…发现了阿雷鲁亚!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.66,0:07:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听过的!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人 是机师来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样么 原来是被联邦抓住了么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.56,0:07:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得下落一直不明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特 让全员集合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开作战会议了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么? 找到阿雷鲁亚了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.42,0:07:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷鲁亚? 谁啊 那家伙是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.95,0:07:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是战友 是战友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.62,0:07:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷鲁亚么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.33,0:07:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.34,0:07:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么中止了Gundam的搜索!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为已经没有必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.98,0:07:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有必要?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.32,0:08:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令部好像是已经撒下饵钓天行者组织出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.01,0:08:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是虽然要对不起地面部队了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.74,0:08:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是试探对方战力的好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了阿雷鲁亚是真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 是王留美传来的确定情报
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.57,0:08:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在要开始救援作战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救援? 怎么救援?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你来考虑方案
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.99,0:08:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪·李·诺莉艾卡 给我们战术预测
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.79,0:08:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他回来了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam 4机的作战就成为可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.23,0:08:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说你也没辙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.77,0:08:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.28,0:08:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了救阿雷鲁亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请穿上这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.58,0:08:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别硬塞给我这样的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的预测什么的 改变不了任何东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.67,0:08:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会让大家暴露在危险之中而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.11,0:09:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不会后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是任务失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不会把错怪在你的头上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们无论是要做怎样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都想把阿雷鲁亚…把战友…解救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 给我们指定战术
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特 等一下现阶段的战力和情况的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.31,0:09:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告诉我么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从王留美处传来了详细数据
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连监禁的人员和场所都…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.59,0:09:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.70,0:09:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能抑止这艘空母的粒子束的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.88,0:09:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔·狄兰迪这么高的能力值
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.06,0:10:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.55,0:10:03.41,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Seravee Cherudim 发射准备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.19,0:10:07.22,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各机师请前往各自的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.97,0:10:09.59,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第1 第2甲板……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于要实战了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不认为你会有出场的机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒真是轻松了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.14,0:10:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰内好像很吵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.06,0:10:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是准备干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.70,0:10:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救回战友 救回战友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战友?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.52,0:10:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战开始 作战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.23,0:10:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要进行战斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seravee 专用火箭炮装备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.83,0:10:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TWIN DRIVE 虽然能启动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.91,0:10:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但离稳定运行还远 别给我用TRANS-AM啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.22,0:10:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.37,0:10:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从斯米拉琪小姐那里传来了任务计划
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂搞什么啊 这份计划…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真大胆的说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.61,0:10:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅300秒的闪电战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.58,0:10:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵… 这才是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.80,0:10:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪·李·诺莉艾卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.45,0:10:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 竟然连我也有分工吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.33,0:10:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这样的确比较方便
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:11:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在说什么 在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自言自语啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.89,0:11:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支援拜托你咯 哈罗君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ptolemaios 进入大气层突入程序
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Seravee Cherudim 出击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.32,0:11:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0043开始任务
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arios保持射出状态待机
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.63,0:11:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从王留美处获得的囚禁阿雷鲁亚的设施中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.80,0:11:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.73,0:11:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽娜!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.83,0:11:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽娜·伊斯玛依露 和阿雷鲁亚在同一设施中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.27,0:11:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN 力场最大展开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.58,0:11:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始突入大气层
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.19,0:11:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐 轨道观察站来电
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到突入大气层的物体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说是运输舰级别
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.25,0:11:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:12:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙飞船整个降落于地面…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.60,0:12:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备炮击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS队抓紧时间准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.65,0:12:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮瑞斯中尉 有敌袭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去确保E-57的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.38,0:12:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.20,0:12:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.09,0:12:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS 机库都被…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.09,0:12:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.33,0:12:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天…天行者的太空船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全炮发射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然不减速
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.41,0:12:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.59,0:12:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN 力场最大程度展开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.01,0:12:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密进入潜水模式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.39,0:12:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突入海底
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌…敌舰进入水中潜行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.23,0:13:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用导弹迎敌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.81,0:13:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种战术 是为了让粒子光束威力减半么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.30,0:13:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 提艾利亚 粒子光束的扩散时间约有300秒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.31,0:13:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这段时间去救出阿雷鲁亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.64,0:13:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解 3分钟就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.01,0:13:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用剩下的2分钟去救另一个人如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.48,0:13:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.28,0:14:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.74,0:14:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个振动是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.50,0:14:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人MS出动了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gherudim 狙击炮战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.10,0:14:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不中也没关系 牵制他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.60,0:14:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.56,0:14:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说哈罗 哥哥在战斗的时候说些什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.41,0:14:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准射击 瞄准射击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All Right
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.99,0:14:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gherudim Gundam 洛克昂·斯特拉特斯 瞄准射击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.58,0:14:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么粒子量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死守这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再接近一点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.69,0:14:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稳如泰山!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.27,0:15:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？ 别的方向的攻击？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.20,0:15:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gherudim 击坠敌机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是新手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.29,0:15:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击中了 击中了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰巧 碰巧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠…靠近不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.95,0:15:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救援队如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.02,0:15:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.69,0:15:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KATARON吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉去确保E-57的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.30,0:15:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.27,0:15:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！ KATARON在解救囚犯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道和天行者联手了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 你为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那个坐标 Arios会来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.02,0:16:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arios?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.55,0:16:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现阿雷鲁亚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.72,0:16:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射Arios
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.89,0:16:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到 发射Arios
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.93,0:16:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密再次潜水
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.67,0:16:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用GN导弹牵制 朝汇合点移动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩下120秒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囚犯们跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.99,0:16:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是刹那他们干的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.11,0:16:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是指定地点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.65,0:17:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了 测试体E-57
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面在进行战斗吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听的见吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离门远一点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.03,0:17:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离远一点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.46,0:17:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.68,0:17:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.51,0:17:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下30秒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.45,0:17:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.68,0:17:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.64,0:17:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不叫那个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.66,0:18:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这真的是你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.61,0:18:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽 玛丽·帕法西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.16,0:18:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽·帕法西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.96,0:18:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽 玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚…刚才的画面是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.94,0:18:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投降吧 E-57
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.16,0:18:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 阿雷鲁亚 时间到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.82,0:18:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 明明玛丽就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.82,0:18:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷鲁亚 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.13,0:18:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷鲁亚 阿雷鲁亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.50,0:18:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽 我一定会回来接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.11,0:19:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有…有3架Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.36,0:19:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.99,0:19:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止射击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优先确保设施的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.60,0:19:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.14,0:19:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam脱离战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退行动开始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.74,0:20:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务完成 任务完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.05,0:20:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同志们的救援成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了G1的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗琳 我从参加救援部队的成员的报告里听来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.71,0:20:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.02,0:20:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队员中好像有人在设施中看到了阿扎帝斯坦第一皇女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽娜·伊斯玛依露大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看…看到玛丽娜了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.18,0:20:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被关押了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,0:20:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我们没能对她进行保护
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.15,0:20:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.53,0:20:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是根据报告 玛丽娜公主被疑似天行者的成员带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.05,0:20:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.25,0:20:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被天行者？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.87,0:21:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.46,0:21:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽娜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.48,0:22:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 提艾利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.06,0:22:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷鲁亚 你怎么被联邦政府抓到的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超人机关的情报…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.33,0:22:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这船真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.05,0:22:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能在水中航行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.18,0:22:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛…洛克昂 你怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.27,0:22:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种反应 我已经腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.64,0:23:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.87,0:23:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是一点没变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.90,0:23:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.69,0:23:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有强行改变的必要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.66,0:23:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 阿雷鲁亚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.17,0:23:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.28,0:23:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为和我扯上关系 把你卷入了不相干的麻烦事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.55,0:23:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 玛丽娜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.64,0:23:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.46,0:23:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你又背负起战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.19,0:23:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非此不可
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.91,0:23:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人 不用战斗的生活方式不也有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.04,0:23:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为我想不出
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.37,0:23:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我的愿望只有通过战斗才能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.57,0:23:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样实在是 太悲伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.39,0:23:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么哭？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.80,0:23:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你不哭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯下过错的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.74,0:24:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能靠自身去矫正
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.78,0:24:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赎罪之旅 也是重生之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.11,0:24:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 战斗的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.68,0:24:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然罪依旧


